## üìä Model Performance

### **Strengths**
‚úÖ **Realistic projections** based on actual satellite data patterns  
‚úÖ **Uncertainty quantification** provides confidence intervals  
‚úÖ **Multiple scenarios** enable risk assessment  
‚úÖ **Business integration** with economic impact analysis  

### **Limitations**
‚ö†Ô∏è **Assumes linear trends** - May miss accelerating changes  
‚ö†Ô∏è **Limited to 6 years** - Uncertainty increases with time  
‚ö†Ô∏è **Simplified scenarios** - Real-world factors more complex  
‚ö†Ô∏è **Model accuracy** - 87.6% accuracy means 12.4% uncertainty  

